{"tid":1329072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"689廣告提示","createTime":"2019-07-18T05:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:56:05.000Z","uid":282542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e8393c412b9a8b21427a108d6b6b2361dfff8ac0","tid":1329072,"uid":282542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"本人平日好想透過支持蘋果廣告客戶<br />\n課金俾包括蘋果日報在內所剩無幾既非紅媒體<br />\n但苦於無買蘋果日報既習慣<br />\n唔知道蘋果有咩廣告<br />\n最近獲悉梁副主席<br />\n位高權重身在曹營心在漢<br />\n依然心系香港<br />\n每日將蘋果由頭到尾刨一次<br />\n並將夠膽係非紅媒體賣廣告既商家名單<br />\n清晰整理公諸於世<br />\n横樹每日都要消費既消費者<br />\n跟住梁副主席既導購指南嚟買嘢<br />\n真系十分方便<br />\n感謝梁振英<br />\n<br />\n呼籲香港市民不要辜負梁振英一片苦心<br />\n多多幫襯非紅媒體廣告客戶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYeKcDF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYeKcDF.jpg&h=711e96a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/leung.cy.108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fleung.cy.108&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAysF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=89a2fab9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/leung.cy.108</a>"}]}